# HackBot2 Disclosure Database
# Format: path!category!severity!description
# severity: INFO LOW MEDIUM HIGH CRITICAL
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
# AI / Bots / Crawler Disclosure (new standards 2024-2025)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
/robots.txt!disclosure!INFO!Crawler directives - may reveal hidden paths
/llms.txt!disclosure!INFO!LLM access policy (ai.robots.txt standard 2024)
/ai.txt!disclosure!INFO!AI crawler policy
/.well-known/ai-plugin.json!disclosure!INFO!OpenAI plugin manifest - reveals API structure
/.well-known/openai.json!disclosure!INFO!OpenAI configuration

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Security / Responsible Disclosure
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
/.well-known/security.txt!disclosure!INFO!Security contact info (RFC 9116)
/security.txt!disclosure!INFO!Security contact info (fallback path)
/.well-known/change-password!disclosure!INFO!Password change URL hint
/humans.txt!disclosure!INFO!Credits file - may reveal tech stack or staff names
/ads.txt!disclosure!INFO!Authorized ad sellers list

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Sitemaps / Discovery
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
/sitemap.xml!disclosure!INFO!Sitemap - reveals all public URLs
/sitemap_index.xml!disclosure!INFO!Sitemap index
/sitemap.xml.gz!disclosure!INFO!Compressed sitemap
/feed/!disclosure!INFO!RSS/Atom feed
/feed.xml!disclosure!INFO!RSS/Atom feed
/atom.xml!disclosure!INFO!Atom feed
/rss.xml!disclosure!INFO!RSS feed
/.well-known/host-meta!disclosure!INFO!Host metadata (WebFinger)

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Environment / Config Files — CRITICAL
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
/.env!config!CRITICAL!Environment file - may contain DB credentials, API keys, secrets
/.env.local!config!CRITICAL!Local environment overrides
/.env.production!config!CRITICAL!Production environment file
/.env.staging!config!CRITICAL!Staging environment file
/.env.development!config!CRITICAL!Development environment file
/.env.backup!config!CRITICAL!Environment file backup
/.env.bak!config!CRITICAL!Environment file backup
/.env.old!config!CRITICAL!Old environment file
/.env.save!config!CRITICAL!Saved environment file
/.env.dist!config!HIGH!Environment template - may reveal variable names
/.env.example!config!MEDIUM!Environment example - reveals expected variables

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
# CMS / Framework Config Files — CRITICAL
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
/wp-config.php!config!CRITICAL!WordPress config - DB credentials
/wp-config.php.bak!config!CRITICAL!WordPress config backup
/wp-config.php.old!config!CRITICAL!WordPress config backup
/wp-config.php~!config!CRITICAL!WordPress config editor backup
/wp-config-sample.php!config!MEDIUM!WordPress config sample
/configuration.php!config!CRITICAL!Joomla config - DB credentials
/configuration.php.bak!config!CRITICAL!Joomla config backup
/LocalSettings.php!config!CRITICAL!MediaWiki config
/settings.php!config!CRITICAL!Drupal config
/config.php!config!CRITICAL!Generic PHP config file
/config/settings.inc.php!config!CRITICAL!PrestaShop database config
/app/etc/local.xml!config!CRITICAL!Magento 1 local config
/app/etc/env.php!config!CRITICAL!Magento 2 environment config
/config/database.php!config!HIGH!Laravel database config
/config/app.php!config!HIGH!Laravel app config - reveals app key
/.htpasswd!config!HIGH!HTTP basic auth credentials
/web.config!config!HIGH!IIS/ASP.NET config (Windows servers)
/config.yml!config!HIGH!Generic YAML config
/config.yaml!config!HIGH!Generic YAML config
/config.json!config!HIGH!Generic JSON config
/config.ini!config!HIGH!Generic INI config
/application.properties!config!HIGH!Java Spring Boot config
/application.yml!config!HIGH!Java Spring Boot YAML config
/appsettings.json!config!HIGH!ASP.NET Core config

